node.title: Police appeal for sightings of missing Taupō man's bike
node.description: Police searching for Taupō man Michael Yewen, who was last seen two months ago, are asking for sightings of his bike.
node.content:
["Police searching for a 50-year-old Taupō man who was last seen two months ago are asking for sightings of his bike.", "", "
Police want to hear about the whereabouts of Taupō man Michael Yewen. Photo: Supplied/ NZ Police
", "Michael Yewen was reported missing on 3 February and police said his family are concerned about his safety.", "He has a black and white E-speed electric bike.", "Anyone with information, or who has seen Yewen or his bike, is being asked to call the police on 105, or Crimestoppers on 0800 555 111."]
